WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:43.550 --> 01:44.750
I got you a box of cold medicine.

01:45.670 --> 01:47.110
Take care of yourself over there.

01:48.390 --> 01:50.150
Make sure you have enough time

01:50.150 --> 01:50.950
between connecting flights.

01:51.229 --> 01:52.270
Your mother

01:52.670 --> 01:54.229
will send someone to pick you up.

01:55.110 --> 01:55.910
I've enabled

01:55.910 --> 01:57.710
international roaming on your phone.

01:58.910 --> 02:01.030
Call me if there's anything urgent.

02:02.550 --> 02:03.630
You're so thoughtful.

02:04.710 --> 02:06.390
Are you so eager to drive me away?

02:06.670 --> 02:07.830
What are you talking about?

02:09.030 --> 02:10.870
Didn't we agree you'd visit your mother

02:11.430 --> 02:13.150
in France over winter break?

02:13.510 --> 02:14.750
Well spoken.

02:15.590 --> 02:17.190
Why didn't you let me go sooner?

02:20.310 --> 02:21.710
With my grandfather gone,

02:22.750 --> 02:24.710
maybe I'm just in the way.

02:29.310 --> 02:30.150
I'll take you to the airport.

02:30.270 --> 02:31.750
No, thanks. I'll take a taxi myself.

03:03.380 --> 03:04.460
Qing, are you here?

03:08.780 --> 03:09.380
Qing.

03:09.380 --> 03:09.980
Hey.

03:12.900 --> 03:13.580
Jinrui.

03:13.860 --> 03:15.480
I'm picking up my wedding photos
from the post office.

03:15.480 --> 03:16.480
Do you want to join me?

03:18.820 --> 03:19.740
Come on.

03:20.660 --> 03:22.300
You're young,
but you stay home too much.

03:22.300 --> 03:23.140
You'll get sick.

03:23.460 --> 03:23.860
Let's go.

03:24.320 --> 03:34.550
[Episode 9]
[The Secret of the Music Box]

03:35.320 --> 03:38.680
[Nanqiao Village]

03:50.650 --> 03:52.370
I've had this car for almost ten years.

03:52.840 --> 03:53.810
It's almost time for a new one.

04:03.330 --> 04:04.840
Bei hung that herself

04:05.560 --> 04:06.810
when the car was first bought.

04:09.470 --> 04:10.110
Jinrui.

04:10.630 --> 04:11.430
Tell me

04:11.430 --> 04:12.950
about Qiao Beiyu when she was a child.

04:14.720 --> 04:16.209
It's been a long time.

04:16.490 --> 04:17.329
I don't remember.

04:18.930 --> 04:20.839
Whenever I asked about Qiao Beiyu,

04:21.089 --> 04:22.530
my family always avoided me.

04:22.810 --> 04:24.840
I really don't know
who else to ask but you.

04:25.000 --> 04:25.970
Tell me.

04:30.720 --> 04:32.560
Bei was brought back to Nanqiao Village
by our grandparents

04:33.330 --> 04:35.280
when she was six years old.

04:36.250 --> 04:37.930
It must be scary for a kid that young

04:38.490 --> 04:39.440
to leave her parents.

04:40.159 --> 04:41.600
I could totally relate,

04:42.090 --> 04:43.810
but she didn't make a fuss.

04:44.390 --> 04:46.840
It's like she knew it wouldn't work.

04:48.000 --> 04:49.560
Even the adults thought

04:49.630 --> 04:51.310
she was adaptable.

04:52.880 --> 04:53.970
But I found out

04:54.330 --> 04:56.600
she always hid herself
and cried at night.

04:59.530 --> 05:01.600
Bei, why are you crying?

05:01.840 --> 05:02.600
Are you okay?

05:04.090 --> 05:05.160
I'm okay.

05:08.510 --> 05:09.670
Let me show you something.

05:47.990 --> 05:50.510
Bei, do you feel better now?

05:55.150 --> 05:56.010
Where have you been?

05:56.630 --> 05:57.330
Ear.

05:58.230 --> 05:59.070
You came out.

06:00.470 --> 06:02.090
I'm going to throw it.

06:02.090 --> 06:03.330
Get ready. It's in.

06:03.510 --> 06:04.990
As the days went by,

06:05.470 --> 06:08.040
Bei got used to life in Nanqiao Village.

06:09.550 --> 06:10.390
But I know

06:11.070 --> 06:12.350
she still hoped

06:12.630 --> 06:14.070
she could live with you.

06:14.070 --> 06:15.470
His long arms and legs

06:15.710 --> 06:17.790
make him ideal for future sports.

06:18.350 --> 06:19.190
Yeah.

06:52.550 --> 06:52.990
Bei.

06:55.710 --> 06:56.190
Bei.

06:57.590 --> 06:58.350
Wait for me.

07:01.030 --> 07:01.830
Let's go home.

07:02.910 --> 07:04.150
Everyone's waiting for you
to start dinner.

07:06.030 --> 07:07.670
Grandma also made your favorite ribs.

07:07.870 --> 07:09.110
She didn't make it for me.

07:09.350 --> 07:10.950
It's for Qingyu and Yu.

07:11.150 --> 07:12.070
I don't want it.

07:12.750 --> 07:15.110
Do you want new clothes, then?

07:16.510 --> 07:18.430
Aunt Fanghao bought you
a lot of beautiful clothes,

07:18.590 --> 07:20.350
shoes, and a new schoolbag.

07:20.830 --> 07:22.750
Qiao Huan would be so envious
if she saw them.

07:24.550 --> 07:25.950
If you don't want them,

07:26.670 --> 07:28.030
I'll go back and tell Aunt Fanghao

07:28.190 --> 07:29.510
to give all of them to Qiao Huan.

07:29.910 --> 07:30.710
I dare you.

07:33.590 --> 07:36.710
Bei, ask your parents

07:37.790 --> 07:38.909
to take you back to Shunyun.

07:40.070 --> 07:41.909
Aunt Fanghao is the easiest to talk to.

07:43.470 --> 07:44.710
Say more nice things to her.

07:45.110 --> 07:46.390
I'm sure they'll say yes.

07:47.430 --> 07:48.710
Grandpa and Grandma said

07:49.110 --> 07:50.750
they'd have Qing take my place

07:50.990 --> 07:53.190
and stay here if I went to Shunyun.

07:53.830 --> 07:55.830
Qing is still young and will cry.

07:57.990 --> 08:00.030
But you also
want to stay with your parents.

08:00.910 --> 08:03.070
It's okay. I have you.

08:04.390 --> 08:06.110
From that moment on, I vowed

08:06.750 --> 08:08.470
to protect Bei

08:09.030 --> 08:10.870
and never let her suffer any injustice.

08:12.190 --> 08:13.430
Soon after you were born,

08:13.790 --> 08:15.470
Bei was brought back to Nanqiao Village.

08:15.990 --> 08:17.550
Although you hadn't
spent much time together,

08:18.190 --> 08:19.270
she always thought

08:19.550 --> 08:20.630
she was the older sister

08:20.950 --> 08:22.790
who should love and protect you.

08:28.190 --> 08:30.750
Before I had a chance
to get to know Qiao Beiyu,

08:31.190 --> 08:32.190
she was gone.

08:33.789 --> 08:35.669
Fortunately,
you were with her in Nanqiao Village.

08:36.909 --> 08:38.549
Jinrui, thank you.

08:40.710 --> 08:41.909
I'm older.

08:42.590 --> 08:43.830
It's my duty.

08:53.070 --> 08:54.030
Wait for me in the car.

08:54.110 --> 08:55.510
I'll show you around this area later.

09:24.890 --> 09:28.170
[Paris, France]

09:30.280 --> 09:31.090
How was it?

09:31.190 --> 09:32.450
Are you tired
from flying all the way here?

09:32.910 --> 09:33.530
I'm alright.

09:34.790 --> 09:36.150
Your mother often mentions you.

09:39.070 --> 09:39.800
I'm Guan Chengyu.

09:40.430 --> 09:41.650
I'm your mother's best friend

09:42.190 --> 09:43.090
and manager.

09:44.790 --> 09:45.570
During this period,

09:45.910 --> 09:47.070
she's preparing

09:47.070 --> 09:48.330
for her music concert.

09:48.990 --> 09:51.010
That's why
she's been in the studio all the time.

09:52.510 --> 09:53.010
It's right here.

10:00.550 --> 10:02.090
This is the piece Anna played

10:02.470 --> 10:03.760
when I first met her.

10:05.110 --> 10:06.880
She had just arrived in France
at that time.

10:07.870 --> 10:09.090
She was working in a restaurant

10:09.270 --> 10:10.360
while looking for opportunities.

10:11.030 --> 10:12.240
And I was still a young man
who hadn't graduated

10:12.390 --> 10:13.050
from university.

10:15.750 --> 10:18.330
She once played this piece

10:18.590 --> 10:20.290
on a public piano
in a French train station

10:20.430 --> 10:21.630
between meal deliveries.

10:21.910 --> 10:22.720
I happened to pass by.

10:25.150 --> 10:26.970
Even people
who don't understand music at all

10:27.590 --> 10:29.090
will be attracted by her.

10:30.590 --> 10:32.640
It's not because
of her impeccable skills

10:33.470 --> 10:34.720
but because of her charisma,

10:37.750 --> 10:40.760
which transcends race, gender,

10:41.270 --> 10:42.360
and language.

10:48.760 --> 10:49.840
See you next time.

10:49.880 --> 10:50.520
Bye.

10:50.570 --> 10:51.240
Bye.

10:51.330 --> 10:51.600
Bye.

10:51.720 --> 10:52.760
Bye.

11:02.290 --> 11:03.090
Gosh.

11:03.090 --> 11:03.570
Mom.

11:12.210 --> 11:14.640
How was it?
Are you tired from the flight?

11:14.640 --> 11:15.120
No.

11:18.350 --> 11:19.590
You've grown so tall.

11:20.630 --> 11:21.790
You're a head taller than me.

11:22.350 --> 11:23.710
I play basketball every day at school,

11:24.670 --> 11:25.310
so I grow quickly.

11:26.750 --> 11:28.930
Here. Check out my studio. Come in.

11:35.330 --> 11:37.210
How about playing a piece?

11:37.880 --> 11:39.600
I'll just spare myself
the embarrassment.

11:42.790 --> 11:43.170
Jinrui.

11:44.310 --> 11:44.880
Move a bit to the left.

11:45.070 --> 11:45.690
Move a bit to the left.

11:46.190 --> 11:46.690
Okay.

11:47.150 --> 11:48.120
A bit higher.

11:49.110 --> 11:50.640
Too high. Lower.

11:51.790 --> 11:53.230
Jinyu, higher.

11:53.230 --> 11:54.090
A bit higher.

11:55.070 --> 11:57.210
Alright. Hang it.

12:03.240 --> 12:04.760
Your grandparents are unbelievable.

12:05.450 --> 12:06.720
Instead of staying at the new house,

12:06.880 --> 12:08.760
they insist on holding
the wedding banquet in the old house.

12:09.050 --> 12:11.170
[Nanqiao High School]
I had to bring Jinrui's stuff over

12:11.170 --> 12:12.880
[Hongzhi Class of 2001]
just for appearances.

12:12.880 --> 12:15.170
Jinrui, are you
from Nanqiao High School too?

12:15.570 --> 12:17.410
Do you know Qiao Beiyu's classmates?

12:19.090 --> 12:20.600
When Bei was in high school,

12:20.840 --> 12:23.570
Jinrui had gone to Huanzhou
for university.

12:23.970 --> 12:25.840
How would he know Bei's classmates?

12:27.360 --> 12:30.000
Qing, help me with the bed sheets.

12:39.410 --> 12:40.810
Which one do you think looks better?

12:41.410 --> 12:43.000
That one looks more festive.

12:43.360 --> 12:44.090
That one.

12:44.410 --> 12:45.410
Okay, let's hang this.

12:50.720 --> 12:51.450
Yanfen.

12:52.520 --> 12:54.360
You've made it through this time.

12:54.760 --> 12:56.360
Just wait for a comfortable life ahead.

12:57.210 --> 12:58.880
I don't have the luck to live one.

12:59.050 --> 13:00.410
Once Jinrui has a baby,

13:00.570 --> 13:02.760
I'll have to help him
take care of the baby.

13:03.240 --> 13:03.880
Yeah.

13:04.000 --> 13:06.170
It's endless worry being a mother.

13:06.570 --> 13:07.970
Yanfen, teach us

13:08.120 --> 13:09.290
how to raise a son

13:09.290 --> 13:10.690
who's as successful as Jinrui.

13:12.290 --> 13:13.840
Jinrui has never troubled me

13:13.930 --> 13:15.240
since he was a child.

13:15.930 --> 13:17.000
His grandparents said

13:17.330 --> 13:19.450
Jinrui came to express his gratitude.

13:19.450 --> 13:20.290
Yeah.

13:20.290 --> 13:21.000
Yanfen.

13:21.120 --> 13:22.330
You're too humble

13:22.330 --> 13:24.600
to say that.

13:24.880 --> 13:26.000
Everyone knows

13:26.000 --> 13:27.840
the Qiao family is well-known

13:27.930 --> 13:30.720
for integrity and virtue.

13:30.840 --> 13:31.810
In the past,

13:31.810 --> 13:33.640
memorial archways would have
been erected at the village entrance.

13:33.640 --> 13:34.520
Yeah.

13:35.930 --> 13:37.120
In my opinion,

13:37.170 --> 13:39.050
the Qiao family has
a strong family tradition.

13:39.120 --> 13:39.840
All the children

13:39.930 --> 13:41.690
are promising.

13:43.170 --> 13:44.690
It's just a pity about Bei.

13:49.090 --> 13:50.120
It's the Chinese New Year.

13:52.880 --> 13:53.930
Yanfen, I remember

13:54.240 --> 13:56.330
the last time our village was so lively

13:56.330 --> 13:58.240
was when Jinrui
was admitted to university.

13:58.240 --> 13:58.930
You're right.

13:59.170 --> 13:59.760
Yeah.

13:59.760 --> 14:00.330
Right?

14:00.480 --> 14:01.520
Back then, Haisheng

14:01.520 --> 14:03.810
bought all the firecrackers
in the village.

14:03.810 --> 14:04.120
Look.

14:04.120 --> 14:05.000
It was so lively.

14:05.000 --> 14:05.290
Yes.

14:05.290 --> 14:06.450
The whole village came.

14:06.520 --> 14:08.290
I remember it was the most lively time

14:08.520 --> 14:09.360
in our village.

14:09.360 --> 14:10.480
Even more lively than Chinese New Year.

14:13.000 --> 14:14.690
Sir, let me pour some liquor for you.

14:15.330 --> 14:16.050
You're too kind.

14:17.330 --> 14:18.000
Sir,

14:18.690 --> 14:20.690
it's my honor to have you here.

14:20.690 --> 14:22.000
You must have a few more drinks today.

14:22.690 --> 14:23.480
You're too kind.

14:24.050 --> 14:24.720
Here.

14:24.810 --> 14:25.330
Okay.

14:25.570 --> 14:26.450
Here. Drink.

14:27.600 --> 14:28.240
Let's enjoy.

14:28.240 --> 14:29.090
Here.

14:29.090 --> 14:30.600
[Admission Letter
of Huanzhou University]

14:30.600 --> 14:31.210
Haisheng.

14:31.840 --> 14:34.120
You two are really something.

14:34.210 --> 14:35.840
You not only nurtured

14:35.840 --> 14:38.520
the first student from our village
to attend a key university,

14:38.840 --> 14:41.520
but also the top scorer in NCEE
for Shunyun County.

14:42.410 --> 14:42.970
Old pal.

14:43.810 --> 14:46.120
You brought honor to the Qiao family.

14:46.120 --> 14:46.450
Yes.

14:46.450 --> 14:48.000
Also to our village.

14:48.170 --> 14:48.480
Here.

14:49.290 --> 14:49.760
Drink up.

14:49.760 --> 14:50.600
Let me have a look.

14:50.640 --> 14:51.760
I have never seen

14:51.760 --> 14:53.240
what a university admission letter
looks like.

14:53.930 --> 14:54.640
So it looks like...

14:54.840 --> 14:55.720
Be careful.

14:55.720 --> 14:56.520
Keep it clean.

14:56.520 --> 14:58.290
I haven't seen enough. Yanfen...

14:58.290 --> 14:59.000
Eat.

15:02.970 --> 15:04.330
Mom, I'm going out to play for a while.

15:04.640 --> 15:05.410
Okay.

15:06.210 --> 15:06.970
Here, sir.

15:07.290 --> 15:07.930
Here's a toast to you.

15:07.930 --> 15:08.330
Okay.

15:08.520 --> 15:09.050
Here.

15:09.520 --> 15:10.520
Light it up yourself.

15:10.930 --> 15:11.880
Okay, I'll light it up now.

15:12.120 --> 15:12.760
Okay.

15:59.390 --> 16:01.590
[Ye Zilin:
Sheng, let's play basketball!]

16:01.590 --> 16:04.270
[Chen Hao: Ming Sheng has gone
to France. Remember?]

16:04.270 --> 16:08.070
[Guan Lan: France!
I want to travel abroad too!]

16:08.070 --> 16:10.000
[Deng Meixi:
France is in a different time zone.]

16:10.000 --> 16:13.110
[Deng Meixi:
I bet Ming Sheng is asleep.]

16:13.110 --> 16:14.590
[Sheng: I'm not asleep.]

16:14.590 --> 16:17.150
[Deng Meixi:
Gosh, Ming Sheng replied to me!]

16:17.150 --> 16:19.030
[Guan Lan: Ming Sheng, how is France?]

16:19.030 --> 16:20.630
[Ye Zilin: Tell us about it!]

16:30.050 --> 16:30.840
It's alright.

16:48.570 --> 16:49.790
[Sheng]

16:58.140 --> 17:00.720
[Qingyu: ?]

17:01.020 --> 17:02.820
[Sheng: It was a mistake.]

17:06.369 --> 17:08.170
[Qingyu: You're childish.]

17:12.050 --> 17:16.319
[Ming Sheng: Why didn't you ask me
if I'm doing well in France?]

17:16.319 --> 17:19.589
[Qingyu: How are you doing, then?]

17:29.840 --> 17:30.970
Hello? Can you hear me?

17:31.720 --> 17:32.840
Can you hear me?

17:33.480 --> 17:34.120
Hello?

17:34.600 --> 17:35.050
Can you hear me?

17:36.270 --> 17:41.070
[Qingyu: I can hear you, but I have
no microphone and can't speak.]

17:41.240 --> 17:42.050
You don't have to speak.

17:42.570 --> 17:44.000
You can just listen to me.

17:59.000 --> 17:59.520
What do you think?

18:00.450 --> 18:01.410
My mom is awesome, right?

18:02.970 --> 18:03.600
Hmm.

18:11.050 --> 18:12.450
When I saw my mom this time,

18:13.890 --> 18:15.850
I think she's completely different

18:17.130 --> 18:19.490
from the painful and depressed image
I remembered of her.

18:20.850 --> 18:22.050
Maybe leaving home

18:22.930 --> 18:23.770
and me

18:24.850 --> 18:26.250
was good for her.

18:27.810 --> 18:28.730
On the contrary,

18:30.050 --> 18:32.130
I was miserable when she left.

18:32.850 --> 18:34.890
And my dad is busy with work every day

18:34.970 --> 18:35.730
and doesn't care about me.

18:37.890 --> 18:38.650
Do you think

18:41.090 --> 18:42.330
I'm completely unnecessary

18:43.250 --> 18:44.610
to them?

18:47.890 --> 18:49.330
No.

18:52.330 --> 18:52.890
Thank you.

19:09.180 --> 19:10.830
Grandma, did you remember it wrong?

19:10.830 --> 19:11.630
No.

19:12.030 --> 19:13.500
I won't remember it wrong.

19:14.030 --> 19:16.660
It's a red leather suitcase

19:16.740 --> 19:20.660
that contains the bed sheet
and quilt cover that I brought as dowry.

19:20.700 --> 19:21.870
They're all good stuff.

19:22.390 --> 19:24.110
I want to pass it on
to my granddaughter-in-law.

19:24.220 --> 19:25.420
Search carefully.

19:25.420 --> 19:26.500
Is this the one?

19:27.150 --> 19:28.550
Yes.

19:29.900 --> 19:30.940
Oh, be careful.

19:32.180 --> 19:33.030
Careful.

19:34.830 --> 19:36.940
Slowly.

19:36.940 --> 19:37.390
Take it.

19:37.390 --> 19:38.740
Okay, let go.

19:47.020 --> 19:51.420
[Qin's notebook]

19:54.070 --> 19:55.260
They're good stuff.

20:02.350 --> 20:04.350
I don't know how much longer
I can hold on.

20:05.310 --> 20:06.310
If I fail,

20:07.150 --> 20:10.350
these words will be proof
I've been here.

20:11.660 --> 20:12.740
I'm not crazy.

20:14.350 --> 20:15.660
My name is Qin Wenqiu.

21:02.810 --> 21:03.210
Mom.

21:03.930 --> 21:04.850
How about I help you?

21:05.090 --> 21:05.770
It's okay.

21:06.250 --> 21:07.490
Yeah, the steps are wrong.

21:07.810 --> 21:08.730
I need to add salt.

21:09.770 --> 21:10.770
You don't have to do anything.

21:11.450 --> 21:12.610
You don't even have to sit here.

21:12.610 --> 21:13.810
It makes me nervous.

21:14.290 --> 21:15.610
I have to help you with the stuffing.

21:16.170 --> 21:17.770
Just stay where you are.

21:18.450 --> 21:20.850
I want to make you
your favorite dumplings.

21:21.250 --> 21:22.330
You don't have to do anything.

21:22.410 --> 21:23.090
Alright?

21:23.290 --> 21:23.970
Okay.

21:24.490 --> 21:25.810
I have to add salt.

21:26.570 --> 21:27.810
No, add water.

21:33.170 --> 21:34.250
Mom, you added too much.

21:34.490 --> 21:34.930
Too much?

21:35.010 --> 21:35.410
Yeah.

21:35.690 --> 21:36.290
It won't come together.

21:36.290 --> 21:37.130
I know what to do.

21:37.450 --> 21:37.930
Add flour.

21:47.130 --> 21:47.530
Mom.

21:50.010 --> 21:52.410
How have you survived
all this time on your own?

21:52.730 --> 21:53.850
Aren't I doing just fine?

21:58.210 --> 21:58.690
Guan?

21:59.370 --> 21:59.930
Ming Sheng.

22:00.170 --> 22:00.530
Come on in.

22:01.010 --> 22:02.730
I happened to pass by Chinatown

22:02.970 --> 22:04.050
and bought some Chinese takeout for you.

22:05.530 --> 22:07.170
Isn't the Chinese New Year
coming soon?

22:07.250 --> 22:08.210
I also brought you a bouquet of flowers.

22:08.370 --> 22:08.890
Thank you.

22:12.660 --> 22:13.150
Guan.

22:13.350 --> 22:14.940
So, you're a fortune teller, huh?

22:14.940 --> 22:16.220
How did you know we haven't eaten?

22:17.310 --> 22:18.660
I know her well.

22:18.940 --> 22:19.980
Your mom's cooking skills

22:20.070 --> 22:22.500
are unbelievable.

22:22.980 --> 22:24.630
She tried
making shacha noodles for us once.

22:24.830 --> 22:26.900
Everyone who ate her cooking
ended up with gastroenteritis.

22:27.350 --> 22:28.150
Enough.

22:28.180 --> 22:29.500
Feel free to trash-talk me
when I'm not around,

22:29.980 --> 22:31.030
but don't do it to my face.

22:31.180 --> 22:31.900
From then on,

22:32.070 --> 22:33.830
I banned her from the kitchen.

22:34.110 --> 22:34.790
You're still on it, huh?

22:35.830 --> 22:36.180
Alright.

22:36.500 --> 22:37.940
We still have some concert prep to do.

22:38.070 --> 22:38.700
I'm leaving.

22:38.830 --> 22:39.150
Okay.

22:39.550 --> 22:40.110
Right, Ming Sheng.

22:40.870 --> 22:42.390
Call me if you're hungry tonight.

22:42.740 --> 22:44.110
Keep her out of the kitchen.

22:44.420 --> 22:46.030
Go ahead, as you're busy.

22:46.150 --> 22:47.070
Keep her out of the kitchen.

22:47.460 --> 22:48.940
Hurry.

22:48.940 --> 22:49.590
Bye.

22:49.700 --> 22:50.350
Oh.

22:50.350 --> 22:51.260
You have got flour on your body.

22:51.260 --> 22:51.630
It's fine. It looks good.

22:51.630 --> 22:52.070
Sorry.

22:52.460 --> 22:53.500
Bye.

22:58.790 --> 22:59.220
Hey.

22:59.830 --> 23:00.150
Hmm?

23:00.980 --> 23:01.590
Put the flowers in a vase.

23:04.700 --> 23:06.310
We're still having dumplings.

23:06.550 --> 23:07.830
After all this work,

23:07.830 --> 23:08.900
we can't give up now.

23:09.310 --> 23:10.260
It's not giving up.

23:10.460 --> 23:11.590
It's called not wasting.

23:13.590 --> 23:15.220
Are you two in cahoots?

23:19.940 --> 23:20.900
Snowflake.

23:21.870 --> 23:22.310
Mom.

23:22.590 --> 23:23.180
Yeah?

23:24.420 --> 23:26.350
You and my dad
have been separated for a long time.

23:27.700 --> 23:30.180
Have you ever thought
about starting over?

23:32.220 --> 23:32.790
No.

23:33.210 --> 23:35.210
I've been through a failed marriage.

23:35.970 --> 23:36.890
I don't want to have another one.

23:37.690 --> 23:38.330
I'm scared.

23:48.730 --> 23:49.330
Ming Sheng.

23:49.610 --> 23:50.170
Hmm?

23:52.130 --> 23:52.850
To be honest,

23:54.730 --> 23:56.250
I'm not a good mother.

23:58.290 --> 23:59.490
Would you hold a grudge

24:01.090 --> 24:01.930
against me?

24:04.210 --> 24:04.810
No.

24:06.530 --> 24:09.330
It's all Ming Qiuxin's fault.

24:11.410 --> 24:12.290
I just want to leave him

24:13.410 --> 24:14.290
as soon as possible.

24:37.930 --> 24:38.730
Qingyu.

24:39.330 --> 24:40.410
Help me.

24:42.370 --> 24:44.050
Mom, why did you buy so many?

24:45.130 --> 24:46.770
I buy it every year
during the Chinese New Year.

24:49.610 --> 24:50.850
Change the water.

24:51.850 --> 24:52.410
Let them spit out the mud.

24:53.170 --> 24:54.490
And kill them
on the Chinese New Year's Eve.

24:57.650 --> 24:58.490
They're so lively.

25:01.290 --> 25:01.930
Mom.

25:02.410 --> 25:04.210
What were you doing
up so late last night?

25:07.330 --> 25:07.810
Me?

25:09.090 --> 25:09.770
I didn't.

25:09.850 --> 25:10.690
You did.

25:13.500 --> 25:14.630
How come I don't remember it?

25:15.390 --> 25:15.940
Qing.

25:20.220 --> 25:20.870
Qing.

25:21.260 --> 25:22.830
The village organized
a holiday daycare center,

25:22.980 --> 25:24.310
and several university graduates,
including me,

25:24.420 --> 25:25.220
helped care for the children.

25:25.260 --> 25:26.030
It's my turn today.

25:26.420 --> 25:28.420
If you're free, come with me.

25:28.940 --> 25:29.420
Sure.

25:30.110 --> 25:31.660
Mom, I'm going out with Jinrui.

25:31.790 --> 25:32.500
Okay.

25:40.590 --> 25:42.260
♪Little star♪

25:42.900 --> 25:46.870
♪Up above the world so high♪

25:47.500 --> 25:51.390
♪Like a diamond in the sky♪

25:52.030 --> 25:55.830
♪Twinkle, twinkle, little star♪

25:56.350 --> 26:00.310
♪How I wonder what you are♪

26:00.830 --> 26:03.790
♪Up above the world so high♪

26:04.420 --> 26:07.310
My best friend
in Nanqiao Village is Bei.

26:08.030 --> 26:10.940
Bei is beautiful and smart.

26:11.220 --> 26:12.390
She's also a good dancer.

26:12.900 --> 26:16.220
I think of her
as my student and daughter.

26:17.260 --> 26:19.740
We live together in Nanqiao Village.

26:20.220 --> 26:21.220
She promised

26:21.590 --> 26:22.180
that

26:22.550 --> 26:24.590
she'd dance at the Huanzhou Theater

26:25.030 --> 26:27.630
and wanted me to be in the audience
to applaud her.

26:29.180 --> 26:29.980
One day,

26:29.980 --> 26:31.700
Bei told me a secret.

26:33.150 --> 26:34.550
She fell in love with Qiao Jinrui.

26:35.310 --> 26:36.870
Bei had a miscarriage.

26:37.390 --> 26:39.660
In fact, Jinrui isn't
from the Qiao family.

26:40.870 --> 26:42.940
In order to inherit
the Qiao family's properties,

26:43.310 --> 26:44.150
Haisheng and Yanfen

26:44.150 --> 26:47.350
adopted Jinrui from the orphanage
without telling anyone.

26:48.550 --> 26:50.590
To keep Jinrui's background
from being exposed

26:51.220 --> 26:53.550
and to preserve
the Qiao family's reputation,

26:54.030 --> 26:55.500
they pinned all the blame

26:56.070 --> 26:58.030
on Bei.

26:59.390 --> 27:00.870
Bei's parents

27:01.180 --> 27:03.070
also rushed back to Nanqiao Village
after hearing the news.

27:03.740 --> 27:04.310
Yanfen.

27:04.790 --> 27:06.420
I have to see Jinrui no matter what.

27:06.870 --> 27:07.870
If I don't see him today,

27:08.150 --> 27:09.550
I'll wait for him
to come back next week.

27:09.630 --> 27:10.420
If I don't see him then,

27:10.420 --> 27:11.150
I'll see him the week after.

27:11.310 --> 27:12.260
I want to see him no matter what.

27:12.390 --> 27:14.150
I have to ask him what happened.

27:14.260 --> 27:15.500
What does it have to do with Jinrui?

27:16.110 --> 27:18.500
Besides, they're cousins.

27:19.260 --> 27:20.180
What proof do you have

27:20.180 --> 27:21.660
to prove that the baby is Jinrui's?

27:22.180 --> 27:23.660
This is just ridiculous.

27:23.790 --> 27:25.390
If the baby isn't Jinrui's,

27:25.390 --> 27:26.940
why can't I meet Jinrui?

27:27.150 --> 27:28.870
Why can't I ask him in person?

27:29.420 --> 27:31.010
If I make a fuss at school or outside,

27:31.010 --> 27:32.050
will it do you, our family,

27:32.050 --> 27:33.370
and Jinrui any good?

27:33.370 --> 27:34.410
I dare you!

27:35.770 --> 27:37.570
Jinrui is the top NCEE scorer.

27:37.770 --> 27:39.890
Everyone says he has a bright future.

27:39.970 --> 27:41.410
Even if it's true,

27:41.530 --> 27:43.010
it's your daughter who seduced my son.

27:43.010 --> 27:43.810
Nonsense!

27:45.730 --> 27:46.850
It takes two to tango.

27:46.850 --> 27:48.410
You do know it takes two to tango.

27:48.450 --> 27:50.890
Enough! Have you two had enough?

27:51.410 --> 27:53.010
Isn't it embarrassing enough?

27:58.460 --> 28:00.630
Bei thought her parents
would side with her,

28:01.310 --> 28:02.390
but all she got

28:03.110 --> 28:04.590
was a slap from her mother.

28:05.740 --> 28:07.150
Bei was very aggrieved.

28:07.790 --> 28:10.150
But she was scared
to tell her parents the truth.

28:10.900 --> 28:12.500
She didn't know

28:13.070 --> 28:14.660
who else she could rely on.

28:15.150 --> 28:16.420
I felt sorry for her.

28:17.110 --> 28:18.660
My poor Bei.

28:20.150 --> 28:22.760
Jinrui probably gave Mom the money.

28:23.030 --> 28:23.980
He pays her every month.

28:24.310 --> 28:26.110
I am partly responsible too.

28:26.550 --> 28:28.830
I failed to guide her as a senior.

28:29.630 --> 28:31.220
That's why she went astray.

28:31.790 --> 28:32.500
[Nanqiao High School, 2001]
Jinrui,

28:32.830 --> 28:34.070
are you from Nanqiao High School too?

28:34.900 --> 28:35.550
Jinrui.

28:36.110 --> 28:36.940
Tell me

28:36.940 --> 28:38.590
about Qiao Beiyu when she was a child.

28:38.700 --> 28:40.350
Bei hung this herself

28:41.180 --> 28:42.700
when the car was first bought.

28:43.180 --> 28:47.310
♪Up above the world so high♪

28:47.900 --> 28:52.790
♪Like a diamond in the sky♪

28:52.790 --> 28:54.700
♪Twinkle, twinkle, little star♪

29:00.310 --> 29:01.070
Do you think

29:01.070 --> 29:02.310
Jinrui knows

29:05.110 --> 29:06.460
the state I'm in?

29:08.740 --> 29:10.220
I think Jinrui knows.

29:11.310 --> 29:13.390
But he never returned
to Nanqiao Village.

29:14.310 --> 29:17.900
The village was abuzz
with the news of Bei's miscarriage.

29:19.070 --> 29:19.630
Yanfen.

29:20.700 --> 29:21.870
I haven't seen you in days.

29:22.150 --> 29:22.740
Here.

29:22.740 --> 29:24.350
Come, sit down and have some seeds.

29:24.350 --> 29:24.700
Sure.

29:24.700 --> 29:25.310
Take this.

29:26.030 --> 29:26.740
Here.

29:28.490 --> 29:29.370
Have you heard of it?

29:29.690 --> 29:31.210
Someone said Bei had a miscarriage

29:31.330 --> 29:33.370
right after returning
from Huanzhou Art School

29:33.530 --> 29:34.570
for winter break.

29:34.850 --> 29:36.930
Yanfen, keep an eye on her.

29:37.490 --> 29:39.810
Bei, where have you been?

29:40.090 --> 29:41.170
Were you fooling around again?

29:41.570 --> 29:42.330
No.

29:43.730 --> 29:45.610
Bei never explained anything

29:46.370 --> 29:48.250
and just endured it alone.

31:01.410 --> 31:01.770
Here.

31:02.130 --> 31:02.890
Here, Jinrui.

31:04.250 --> 31:04.890
Thank you, Grandma.

31:06.930 --> 31:07.850
Yu, hurry.

31:08.250 --> 31:08.970
Thank you, Grandma.

31:10.330 --> 31:10.650
Okay.

31:11.210 --> 31:12.170
Eat while it's hot.

31:13.330 --> 31:14.050
Have some liquor.

31:17.570 --> 31:18.130
Qing.

31:18.610 --> 31:21.370
You haven't left your room in two days

31:21.730 --> 31:23.890
except to eat.

31:24.370 --> 31:25.210
This can't work.

31:25.490 --> 31:26.450
The Chinese New Year
is coming soon.

31:26.970 --> 31:29.330
More and more relatives
are visiting us.

31:29.650 --> 31:31.890
Uncle Zhang even asked about you today.

31:32.890 --> 31:34.090
I do my homework in my room.

31:34.410 --> 31:35.570
I don't know them either.

31:37.090 --> 31:39.010
Others asked about you out of kindness.

31:39.090 --> 31:41.010
Greeting them cheerfully

31:41.130 --> 31:42.130
is what juniors should do.

31:42.930 --> 31:44.210
It's not like school starts tomorrow.

31:44.370 --> 31:45.690
Why hurry with your homework?

31:46.090 --> 31:46.850
Yeah.

31:47.130 --> 31:48.490
You have to get married sooner or later.

31:48.970 --> 31:49.890
In my opinion,

31:50.210 --> 31:53.410
Qing was doing well
at Shunyun No. 1 High School.

31:53.570 --> 31:54.610
Why transfer?

31:55.330 --> 31:57.210
Big cities like Huanzhou

31:57.370 --> 31:59.130
have all kinds of people.

31:59.610 --> 32:01.770
Yu is a boy.

32:01.930 --> 32:03.610
It's good for him
to go there and see the world.

32:03.850 --> 32:04.970
Qing is a girl.

32:05.130 --> 32:06.210
What if she goes bad?

32:06.730 --> 32:07.370
Yanfen.

32:08.210 --> 32:09.610
We heard
that the teaching quality in Huanzhou

32:09.610 --> 32:11.250
is pretty good.

32:11.570 --> 32:13.530
I just want Qingyu to work hard

32:13.770 --> 32:15.690
and see if she can
get into a good university.

32:16.930 --> 32:19.210
She's usually just busy reading books

32:19.490 --> 32:20.410
and doesn't care about anything else.

32:21.490 --> 32:22.530
I'm not too worried about her.

32:25.390 --> 32:28.790
Oh, do you know
what's going on in her head?

32:29.740 --> 32:31.630
Don't blame me for being blunt.

32:31.790 --> 32:34.110
Girls have a lot on their minds
these days.

32:34.660 --> 32:35.870
Some precocious kids

32:36.030 --> 32:37.700
go astray at 16 or 17 years old.

32:37.980 --> 32:39.500
You really need to be careful.

32:39.740 --> 32:42.630
Be careful of Qing
being led astray in Huanzhou.

32:44.310 --> 32:47.420
Hey, Qiao Beiyu
grew up in Nanqiao Village.

32:48.220 --> 32:49.550
Who led her astray?

32:54.550 --> 32:55.740
The Qiao family

32:55.790 --> 32:57.740
is known to be good.

32:58.310 --> 32:59.940
We both treated Bei

33:00.030 --> 33:01.310
with our hearts and soul

33:01.310 --> 33:02.550
and raised her like our own daughter.

33:03.220 --> 33:04.630
Everyone in the village knew.

33:05.590 --> 33:06.500
If you want to talk
about being led astray,

33:07.420 --> 33:08.350
it was most likely

33:09.500 --> 33:10.980
Jiangsheng's wife who led her astray.

33:12.070 --> 33:13.460
Why did you shift the focus to me again?

33:14.700 --> 33:15.350
Jinrui.

33:15.740 --> 33:17.420
Is what Aunt Yanfen said true?

33:18.030 --> 33:20.220
Did Qiao Beiyu's being led astray
have anything to do with you?

33:23.900 --> 33:24.870
Ask around.

33:25.220 --> 33:26.070
No one

33:26.220 --> 33:27.660
can find fault

33:28.310 --> 33:29.790
with Jinrui's character.

33:30.790 --> 33:31.420
Yeah.

33:31.630 --> 33:32.940
If something's wrong with Jinrui,

33:33.220 --> 33:34.310
would Xiaoyun's parents

33:34.420 --> 33:35.870
marry such a good daughter like Xiaoyun

33:35.870 --> 33:36.700
to us?

33:37.110 --> 33:39.350
Their family holds leadership positions.

33:39.350 --> 33:40.260
They're well-off.

33:40.980 --> 33:42.590
Their willingness to marry us

33:42.790 --> 33:46.350
shows that Jinrui
is capable and reliable.

33:46.740 --> 33:49.590
Qing, good thing it's all family here.

33:49.900 --> 33:51.550
What would an outsider think

33:52.110 --> 33:52.900
about your remarks?

33:54.150 --> 33:54.940
Right, Dad?

33:56.900 --> 33:57.420
Lusheng.

33:57.900 --> 34:00.500
You're the head of your family.

34:00.900 --> 34:02.500
Say something.

34:06.660 --> 34:07.830
They're all your elders.

34:08.420 --> 34:09.310
How could you speak like that?

34:15.310 --> 34:16.790
She always spoke
in a soft and gentle manner

34:16.980 --> 34:18.550
when she was little.

34:18.830 --> 34:20.260
Why did she change suddenly?

34:20.350 --> 34:21.790
Someone must have led her astray.

34:22.350 --> 34:23.260
She's dead,

34:23.630 --> 34:25.500
but it doesn't mean
the past didn't happen.

34:30.350 --> 34:30.739
Enough.

34:36.110 --> 34:36.940
Alright.

34:37.389 --> 34:38.739
Don't blame Qingyu.

34:39.460 --> 34:41.150
It's a delicate time for her.

34:41.389 --> 34:43.070
It's okay for her
to have some weird ideas.

34:44.610 --> 34:45.170
Qingyu.

34:45.810 --> 34:47.210
I know you feel sorry for your sister.

34:47.850 --> 34:49.449
Everybody's sad about Beiyu.

34:49.850 --> 34:52.010
But everyone chooses their own path.

34:52.690 --> 34:53.690
You can't blame others.

34:54.810 --> 34:55.409
I think

34:55.929 --> 34:57.170
Beiyu must want everyone

34:57.170 --> 34:58.370
to remember her in a good way.

34:59.930 --> 35:01.090
Let's just forget

35:01.730 --> 35:02.770
about the past.

35:08.660 --> 35:09.150
Alright.

35:10.150 --> 35:11.220
It's all in the past.

35:12.460 --> 35:13.590
Stop talking about it and eat.

35:17.740 --> 35:18.900
Here's a toast to you, Dad.

35:41.930 --> 35:42.610
Pour some water.

35:52.850 --> 35:53.410
Qingyu.

35:54.330 --> 35:55.090
Let me remind you.

35:55.370 --> 35:56.930
Watch your mouth these couple of days.

35:58.690 --> 35:59.770
Don't cause trouble.

36:00.730 --> 36:01.970
You're old enough

36:02.450 --> 36:03.530
to know your priorities.

36:04.210 --> 36:05.890
We're all busy
with Jinrui's wedding right now.

36:06.090 --> 36:07.250
Don't cause any scene.

36:07.610 --> 36:08.170
Why?

36:09.410 --> 36:10.290
Why?

36:10.610 --> 36:12.130
It's because Jinrui
is the first university student

36:12.570 --> 36:14.010
and the most promising child
in the village.

36:16.650 --> 36:17.090
Also,

36:17.810 --> 36:19.090
you transferred to another school
because he helped you

36:19.210 --> 36:20.130
deliver your transcript.

36:20.850 --> 36:22.530
Maybe you'll need his help
to find you a job in the future.

36:25.010 --> 36:26.370
What about what he did to Beiyu?

36:27.970 --> 36:29.210
Who? Jinrui and Beiyu?

36:30.690 --> 36:31.450
How did you know?

36:31.450 --> 36:32.490
Who did you hear that from?

36:32.490 --> 36:34.130
It's all nonsense.

36:42.010 --> 36:42.610
Well,

36:43.610 --> 36:45.170
you just have too much of a good temper.

36:46.330 --> 36:47.890
You do everything your wife says.

36:48.330 --> 36:49.410
Look at what Qing

36:49.410 --> 36:50.730
has become from her teaching.

36:51.810 --> 36:52.770
A man

36:54.290 --> 36:56.170
should call the shots in his family.

37:02.210 --> 37:03.090
Whatever you know,

37:03.090 --> 37:04.450
keep it to yourself.

37:04.810 --> 37:05.890
Act like you don't know.

37:09.780 --> 37:10.950
Qiao Beiyu alone is enough

37:11.180 --> 37:12.300
to make people gossip.

37:12.630 --> 37:14.150
If you get Jinrui involved,

37:15.180 --> 37:15.950
your grandpa

37:15.950 --> 37:16.990
will be humiliated.

37:17.550 --> 37:18.260
Won't that be good?

37:18.660 --> 37:20.660
No one in the Qiao family is innocent.

37:20.740 --> 37:22.030
They wronged Qiao Beiyu.

37:22.340 --> 37:23.910
Don't you want justice for Qiao Beiyu?

37:23.910 --> 37:24.300
No.

37:25.590 --> 37:26.220
I don't want to.

37:29.210 --> 37:29.930
Justice?

37:30.730 --> 37:31.570
Not everything is fair.

37:32.810 --> 37:33.810
Everyone wants justice.

37:34.730 --> 37:35.770
Could anyone handle all of it?

37:36.810 --> 37:37.650
If you're really capable,

37:38.290 --> 37:39.410
get into a good university

37:39.410 --> 37:40.450
and prove yourself.

37:48.730 --> 37:50.130
I'm doing it for your own good.

37:51.930 --> 37:53.690
Your wife is an outsider after all.

37:56.530 --> 37:58.530
Only we are family.

38:02.610 --> 38:03.330
Enough.

38:03.970 --> 38:05.050
It's late. I'm going back.

38:06.330 --> 38:07.210
Haisheng, be careful.

38:11.730 --> 38:12.530
Be careful.

38:25.570 --> 38:26.210
All you do

38:28.130 --> 38:29.210
is drink!

38:29.730 --> 38:30.770
Didn't you say it yourself?

38:31.570 --> 38:32.450
Haisheng drinks all day long

38:32.450 --> 38:33.490
and does nothing else.

38:35.370 --> 38:35.850
Qiao Lusheng.

38:36.050 --> 38:36.530
Hmm.

38:37.770 --> 38:38.570
I warn you.

38:39.370 --> 38:40.650
Don't pick up bad habits.

38:42.770 --> 38:43.690
You hear me?

38:45.490 --> 38:45.970
Sure.

38:58.930 --> 38:59.450
Jinrui.

39:00.690 --> 39:01.930
Is my groomsman suit ready?

39:03.730 --> 39:04.290
Yes.

39:05.890 --> 39:06.850
Take it.

39:08.650 --> 39:09.650
I was planning to deliver it

39:09.650 --> 39:10.690
to your house tonight.

39:11.090 --> 39:12.450
You came just in time.

39:13.890 --> 39:14.890
Congratulations, Jinrui.

39:16.010 --> 39:16.810
If Beiyu were still alive,

39:17.610 --> 39:18.690
she would be happy for you.

39:21.290 --> 39:22.890
It's my fault
for failing to protect Beiyu.

39:24.010 --> 39:25.930
Otherwise, she wouldn't have...

39:26.050 --> 39:27.250
Don't over-think.

39:28.050 --> 39:28.850
Everything will be fine.

39:29.850 --> 39:30.410
Bye.

39:40.010 --> 39:40.570
Feihai!

39:42.610 --> 39:43.170
Qingyu?

39:43.970 --> 39:44.530
What's the matter?

39:45.650 --> 39:46.730
Are you attending the wedding?

39:48.090 --> 39:49.090
Jinrui is getting married.

39:49.090 --> 39:50.010
Of course I'll be there.

39:51.170 --> 39:52.730
What if Beiyu doesn't want you
to attend it?

39:54.490 --> 39:56.890
Qiao Jinrui wronged Qiao Beiyu.

39:56.890 --> 39:58.410
If you really see Beiyu as your friend,

39:58.610 --> 39:59.850
you shouldn't attend for her sake.

40:03.450 --> 40:05.450
Do you have some misunderstanding
about him?

40:05.450 --> 40:06.330
It's not a misunderstanding.

40:06.610 --> 40:07.730
He's a hypocrite.

40:07.890 --> 40:09.530
His kindness to Beiyu is all fake.

40:09.530 --> 40:10.090
Qingyu.

40:11.010 --> 40:11.490
I know

40:12.450 --> 40:13.530
Beiyu's death was sudden,

40:14.010 --> 40:15.450
so you can't accept it yet

40:16.050 --> 40:17.010
and want to find someone to blame

40:17.010 --> 40:18.010
for her misfortunes.

40:18.490 --> 40:19.170
But

40:20.170 --> 40:21.250
it can't be Jinrui.

40:21.610 --> 40:22.490
If Beiyu knew

40:23.250 --> 40:24.210
you're hurting Jinrui

40:24.210 --> 40:25.410
in her name,

40:25.690 --> 40:26.610
she would be very disappointed.

40:26.970 --> 40:27.610
What do you know?

40:28.130 --> 40:29.210
You all have no idea!

40:30.130 --> 40:30.770
Qingyu!

40:42.090 --> 40:43.290
Everybody's sad about Beiyu.

40:43.690 --> 40:45.850
But everyone chooses their own path.

40:46.530 --> 40:47.530
You can't blame others.

40:48.210 --> 40:50.090
Do you have some misunderstanding
about him?

40:51.090 --> 40:51.770
But

40:52.770 --> 40:53.850
it can't be Jinrui.

40:54.210 --> 40:55.090
If Beiyu knew

40:55.850 --> 40:56.810
you're hurting Jinrui

40:56.810 --> 40:58.090
in her name,

40:58.290 --> 40:59.290
she would be very disappointed.

41:01.050 --> 41:02.130
Everyone wants justice.

41:03.130 --> 41:03.970
Not everything is fair.

42:15.130 --> 42:15.890
What a coincidence.

42:21.210 --> 42:22.610
Turns out the accessory in your car

42:23.130 --> 42:24.810
is the same as Beiyu's music box.

42:26.610 --> 42:28.730
Where did you find these?

42:29.050 --> 42:30.570
I had a dream last night.

42:31.170 --> 42:32.450
Qiao Beiyu told me

42:32.610 --> 42:33.930
there's a music box in the attic.

42:34.690 --> 42:36.570
And I did find it the next day.

42:37.010 --> 42:38.610
Do you think she came to me in my dream

42:39.410 --> 42:41.450
because she had some unfulfilled wish?

42:42.410 --> 42:43.770
What does she want to tell me?

42:44.210 --> 42:45.010
Don't talk nonsense.

42:45.530 --> 42:47.050
What dream?

42:47.610 --> 42:48.810
That's you in the photo, right?

42:50.050 --> 42:50.850
Of course not.

42:51.010 --> 42:51.770
How could it be?

42:52.930 --> 42:53.570
Jinrui.

42:54.570 --> 42:57.770
Lying has consequences.

43:30.780 --> 43:34.470
♪Perhaps♪

43:34.980 --> 43:40.680
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

43:41.820 --> 43:47.220
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

43:48.220 --> 43:53.780
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

43:59.450 --> 44:03.120
♪In the future♪

44:03.580 --> 44:09.300
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

44:10.800 --> 44:15.870
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

44:17.120 --> 44:22.280
♪That never expires♪

44:25.880 --> 44:30.350
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

44:31.350 --> 44:35.020
♪Is your name♪

44:35.520 --> 44:40.620
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

44:41.700 --> 44:44.920
♪At first sight♪

44:45.350 --> 44:48.630
♪The future has been determined♪

44:49.320 --> 44:54.880
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

44:55.980 --> 44:59.520
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

44:59.980 --> 45:03.920
♪Is a place♪

45:04.220 --> 45:09.780
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

45:10.450 --> 45:13.820
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

45:14.150 --> 45:17.620
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

45:18.150 --> 45:24.220
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
